&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be the technical owner of features from design to implementation. &lt;/strong&gt;Take ownership of ongoing support and ensure high-quality delivery throughout the development lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage individual project priorities, deadlines, code quality and deliverables. &lt;/strong&gt;Participate in occasional on-call duties to keep software systems up and running smoothly.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner with cross-functional teams including engineers, product managers and designers. &lt;/strong&gt;Collaborate to engineer real solutions that drive growth and innovation in the hospitality industry.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work with cutting-edge technology stack. &lt;/strong&gt;Utilize tools like Python, Django, and modern cloud infrastructure to build scalable solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
