&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Customer Support Team at SevenRooms partners directly with hospitality operators around the world to deliver best-in-class customer support. Whether it&#39;s troubleshooting an issue, explaining how a feature works, or helping clients get the most out of our platform, we’re here to ensure they succeed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shifts: &lt;/strong&gt; Full-Time&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Team Lead, Customer Support leads our UK-based support team, ensuring hospitality operators receive fast, effective, and empathetic assistance. This role oversees day-to-day team operations, supports the growth and development of our support representatives, and helps maintain the high standard of service our customers rely on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’re excited about this opportunity because you will…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
